        {
            "id": 6008753,
            "title": "億光5月營收16億元雙減 仍看旺下半年",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>LED 廠億光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2393:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2393\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2393-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日公告 5 月營收為 16.08 億元，呈年月雙減；累計前 5 月營收為 84.2 億元，較去年同期減少 3.8%；億光表示，由於國際局勢不穩定，下半年營收展望雖有下調，但 LED 產業供需仍在可控範圍，傳統旺季可望到來。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008753%2Fl%2Fe4dedd64dfac8010e418287fd73c259f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">億光5月營收16億元年月雙減 面對關稅仍看旺下半年。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>億光 5 月營收 16.08 億元，月減 10.9%、年減 14.2%；累計前 5 月營收為 84.2 億元，較去年同期減少 3.8%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>億光日前表示，預期第二季營收與去年相當，原先預期全年可以呈個位數成長，但面臨因國際局勢不確定性增加而調整，展望後市，LED 產業部分，90 天關稅緩衝期並未大幅拉貨，傳統旺季可望到來，而不可見光、車用產品仍在成長，可望成為未來主力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
