        {
            "id": 6008752,
            "title": "是方受惠新客戶進駐機房 5月營收年增逾5成寫新猷",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>是方 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6561:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6561\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6561-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日公告 5 月營收達 4.46 億元，年月雙增，其中，年增超過 5 成，寫下歷史單月新高紀錄。是方指出，5 月營收表現亮眼，主因為新客戶進駐 LY2 機房，新增一次性營收。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008752%2Fl%2F3c3a8c5e14415116e916b16dc7defcfe.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">是方LY2機房。(圖：是方提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>是方 5 月營收 4.46 億元，月增 25.78%，年增 56.42%，寫下歷史單月新高；累計今年前 5 月營收 17.54 億元，年增 23.66%。是方指出，受惠 AI 需求暢旺，新客戶進駐機房，因此新增一次性營收，帶動 5 月營收表現。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>是方看好 AI 發展，各行各業對於 AI 資料中心需求逐步提升，且需要具高承載、水冷及散熱能力的資料中心提供服務，而台灣 AI 伺服器可於本地供應鏈生產，有不受關稅影響的優勢，因此在台灣投資 AI 算力中心提供跨國區域型服務，更具市場競爭力。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>展望第二季，是方提到，隨著 AI 需求持續強勁，且聯雲智能資料中心在散熱與載重上皆符合 AI 所需的高規格需求，預期第二季營收與獲利皆有望優於第一季，整體營運展望正向。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
